				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-T%E1%BB%AD-Chi/B%E1%BB%91c-to%C3%A1n-t%E1%BB%AD-T%E1%BB%8Bch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%E1%BB%91ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Du/poem-TabVA_G3m_R73nGvj8srMg">Bốc toán tử - Tịch thượng tống Vương Ngạn Du - 卜算子－席上送王彥猷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-T%E1%BB%AD-Chi/author-nzYvzfRmo_6cp61oWHXvHg">Chu Tử Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Di%E1%BB%87p-m%C3%A3-nhi-ph%C3%BA/poem-srqlqH7ka2gM2RBBIsxudQ">Diệp mã nhi phú - 葉馬兒賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-T%C3%A2y-L%C3%A2m-b%C3%ADch/poem-F9u6th-RZwOC_TiudthKcA">Đề Tây Lâm bích - 題西林壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-B%C3%ACnh-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-th%C3%A0nh-Phi%C3%AAn-S%E1%BB%A9-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Trang-Ho%C3%A0ng-Ki%C3%AAm-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-thuy%C3%AAn-th%C4%83ng-H%C3%A0-T%C4%A9nh-tu%E1%BA%A7n-ph%E1%BB%A7-l%C6%B0u/poem-pNK05RAt_HtR3yW1oIEuhw">Hoạ Quảng Bình đồng thành Phiên Sứ Ngọc Trang Hoàng Kiêm tiên sinh thuyên thăng Hà Tĩnh tuần phủ lưu giản nguyên vận kỳ 1 - 和廣平同城藩使玉莊黃兼先生銓陞河靜巡撫留柬原韻其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-Hi%E1%BB%83u-v%E1%BB%8Dng-k%C3%BD-thi-ki%C3%AAm-tr%C3%ACnh-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-S%C6%A1n/poem-1q5chCI59_b0RngAPpRpUA">Hoạ Việt Thạch “Hiểu vọng” ký thi, kiêm trình Tượng Sơn - 和越石曉望寄詩兼呈象山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-ioE9gUDRRK0CF1f-0I-Dgw">Châu Hải Đường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/S%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%C3%AAn/poem-caQxsCjfGjSxmXxNvnKosQ">Sương thiên - 霜天</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-k2nQ5fnr9ZRE2MDraIsNMQ">Nguyễn Tư Giản</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/T%E1%BA%A3o-thu-d%E1%BB%AF-ch%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%AD-%C4%91%C4%83ng-Qu%E1%BA%AFc-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A2y-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-quan-thi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-ujaZBy7JSAK5yV8opw4kUw">Tảo thu dữ chư tử đăng Quắc Châu tây đình quan thiếu - 早秋與諸子登虢州西亭觀眺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Tr%C6%B0ng-Minh/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-H%E1%BB%93/poem--LJeHmbDXD_jyl8MvTvcKA">Thạch Hồ - 石湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Tr%C6%B0ng-Minh/author-xHa000oq0fYTe8iRr83EKg">Văn Trưng Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Minh-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-D%C6%B0-Qu%C3%BD/poem-1hyRItLEA1i4A9mVsfb2iQ">Tống Đại Minh quốc sứ Dư Quý - 送大明國使余貴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%B4n-Vu-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%8B-chi%C3%AAu-%E1%BA%A9m-m%C3%B4ng-to%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%A1ch-Ninh-B%C3%ACnh-b%E1%BB%91-ch%C3%A1nh-tr%C3%AD-s%E1%BB%B1-C%C3%BAc-L%C3%A2m-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-t%E1%BA%B7ng/poem-nRU4m1fpmejkF687WUakvA">Vương tôn Vu Hương thị chiêu ẩm mông toạ khách Ninh Bình bố chánh trí sự Cúc Lâm tiên sinh đề tặng hoạ vận dĩ đáp - 王孫芋香氏招飲蒙坐客寧平布政致事菊林先生題贈和韻以答</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br></d